{"tid":1177751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生疑亂過馬路 遭巴士撞倒頭受傷","createTime":"2019-05-30T02:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T03:20:22.000Z","uid":3090,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"101df0a29acbbd3c694000073fbac93fda24425b","tid":1177751,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVcdcZo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVcdcZo.png&h=d2b2a07a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KCD8xK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KCD8xK.png&h=c0148176&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcW16jq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcW16jq.png&h=2af153c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上7時49分，一輛新巴在北角寶馬山道落斜，至賽西湖公園外，撞倒一名16歲男學生。現場消息稱，傷者清醒倒卧地上，有熱心途人上前急救，稍後再由救護員將他送院。肇事巴士擋風玻璃碎裂，車長在場協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n駕駛七人車送兩名子女上學的吳太表示，她駕車沿路上斜，男生突然走出過馬路，她及時煞車，但迎面落斜的巴士煞掣不及，將男生撞飛地上，他頭部受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n吳太說：「我兩個小朋友喺車上睇卡通片，唔知發生車禍。當我大叫，佢哋見到前面瞓咗個男生先至識驚。後來我好朋友嚟到，幫我湊走小朋友返學」。她留在現場協助調查。"},{"pid":"6e76e515ad249303ac2c7cb8dbb776f71852f262","tid":1177751,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"英勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989a32618031fa19341eba4a9f3537939736d18e","tid":1177751,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"7人車都煞到<br />\n巴士煞唔到？"},{"pid":"84aea6ee416fcddb6d9403dca1cda2709b069706","tid":1177751,"uid":208689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"989a32618031fa19341eba4a9f3537939736d18e","tid":1177751,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"7人車都煞到<br />\n巴士煞唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？"},{"pid":"90a335ad7977133d9a9d232112f6e445c4dfd904","tid":1177751,"uid":33443,"like":2